(VERSION 1.2) (February 2010)

CS_Ship_TWS2, a map by The Wormhole Studios

This map has more rooms, more details, better lighting and better VIS then the older version here: http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/125473

------------------------------------
HOW TO INSTALL
------------------------------------

1. Put the files "cs_ship_tws2.nav" & "cs_ship_tws2" here:
"X:\Programs\Steam\SteamApps\ (account name) \counter-strike source\cstrike\maps"

2. Start up Counter-Strike: Source and play CS_Ship_TWS2 !
